add_allowed_domain

.SH Name
.SP 5 5
add_allowed_domain -  Adds a string to the list of domains to be checked by the npc when it  moves to see if it's allowed to be in that room, eg.
.EP

.SH Syntax
.SI 5
void add_allowed_domain(string domain)
.EI

.SH Parameters
.SI 5
%^BOLD%^domain%^RESET%^ - the name of the domain to be added

.EI

.SH Defined in
.SI 5
/std/npc/surface_decorator.c
.EI

.SH Description
.SP 5 5

Adds a string to the list of domains to be checked by the npc when it 
moves to see if it's allowed to be in that room, eg. "/d/guilds" or 
"Bes_Pelargic"

.EP

